# 1. Ignore absolutely everything by default (this catches all extension-less binaries)
*

# 2. Un-ignore all directories (so Git can actually look inside your folders)
!*/

# 3. Un-ignore all files that have an extension (keeps .c, .txt, .md, .h, etc.)
!*.*

# 4. Un-ignore specific extension-less files that are actually useful
!Makefile
